{"tid":500612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青提「聖誕」：屌你老母","createTime":"2017-12-16T03:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T15:48:33.000Z","uid":76674,"like":206,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fdb6acfd9133ec4b0719fb7034b4333868cd00","tid":500612,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20121218/large/1355814467_b68d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20121218%2Flarge%2F1355814467_b68d.jpg&h=05bd91ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有Hard Feeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"d9793c1a94671406b3489371b74cf3909f3e2ae8","tid":500612,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef803e59826de43bb9e4ab03a3cd97164211f1d3","tid":500612,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c268a4fe67d3f90be473cdf69ff8b1b9bf6484","tid":500612,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcd0e81e341cb03e4f49c459f14b9e1f011dde9","tid":500612,"uid":65587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1bd26b96a11b4dc44592481579770048e80b3b","tid":500612,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0